
Tamiko Aiko learns how to become a woman at the age of 16. She would always hold the house down when her mama wasn't home. Knowing their circumstances, she knew her mother wasn't coming back. Everyone is trying to get out of the hood but in realization the people of New Orleans, Louisiana knew its hard to get out.
Tamiko meets a boy around her age who slangs a couple rocks and pop a couple bands.They both want out the hood so they  cross paths at the wrong time. This is no ordinary love story,its a tale of life